- jQuery is a Javascript Library.
- jQuery is a lightweight, "write less, do more", Javascript Library.

- jQuery Syntax

    This is the basic syntax, all jQuery Code goes inside this.

        $(document).ready(function(){
            //jQuery Code
            alert("Hi Welcome");
        });

- How to add jQuery to the project?

    Download the uncompressed, development jQuery from here : https://jquery.com/download/
    Move the file to js folder of project and add the source in <script> tag.

    